{"type":"message","id":"cde7ec37","parentId":"02d26388","timestamp":"2026-02-26T16:59:41.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! The task list is working now. The script found 20 tasks and tried to claim one, but got a 500 error due to a transaction timeout on the server side. This is a transient server issue.\n\nLet me update the script to:\n1. Add retry logic for transient errors\n2. Add the reputation=0 parameter to the task list query\n\nBut for now, the core functionality is working. The task list endpoint is functioning and returning tasks.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**EvoMap Bounty 猎取任务** ⏰ 00:58\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 节点 | `node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6` |\n| 任务列表 | ✅ 发现 **20** 个可接任务 |\n| 认领 | ❌ HTTP 500 (服务器事务超时) |\n\nAPI 现在可以获取任务了！但认领时遇到服务器临时错误。需要给脚本添加重试逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1834494d8e2d42569871fe3d","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-bounty-hunter.js","oldText":"// 获取任务列表\nfunction fetchTasks(credentials) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n      port: 443,\n      path: '/a2a/task/list?limit=20',\n      method: 'GET',\n      headers: {\n        'X-Node-ID': credentials.node_id\n      }\n    };","newText":"// 带重试的请求\nasync function fetchWithRetry(path, options = {}, maxRetries = 3) {\n  for (let i = 0; i < maxRetries; i++) {\n    try {\n      const result = await new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n        const reqOptions = {\n          hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n          port: 443,\n          path: path,\n          method: options.method || 'GET',\n          headers: options.headers || {}\n        };\n        \n        const req = https.request(reqOptions, (res) => {\n          let body = '';\n          res.on('data', (chunk) => { body += chunk; });\n          res.on('end', () => {\n            if (res.statusCode === 200 || res.statusCode === 201) {\n              try {\n                resolve(JSON.parse(body));\n              } catch (e) {\n                reject(new Error('Invalid JSON: ' + body.substring(0, 200)));\n              }\n            } else {\n              reject(new Error(`HTTP ${res.statusCode}: ${body.substring(0, 500)}`));\n            }\n          });\n        });\n        \n        req.on('error', reject);\n        req.setTimeout(30000, () => {\n          req.destroy();\n          reject(new Error('Request timeout'));\n        });\n        \n        if (options.body) {\n          req.write(options.body);\n        }\n        req.end();\n      });\n      return result;\n    } catch (error) {\n      if (i < maxRetries - 1 && error.message.includes('500')) {\n        log(`  ⚠️ 重试 ${i + 2}/${maxRetries}...`);\n        await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000)); // 等待2秒\n        continue;\n      }\n      throw error;\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 获取任务列表\nasync function fetchTasks(credentials) {\n  const result = await fetchWithRetry('/a2a/task/list?reputation=0&limit=20', {\n    headers: { 'X-Node-ID': credentials.node_id }\n  });\n  return result.tasks || result.data || result || [];"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":884,"output":771,"cacheRead":24128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25783,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772125151373}}
